# JAVA MINI PROJECT DOCUMENTATION

## Banking System Simulation (GUI + MySQL)

---

# 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

The **Banking System Simulation** is a desktop-based application developed using **Core Java (Swing)** and **MySQL database (JDBC)**. The system replicates real-world banking operations such as user authentication, account handling, transactions, and audit tracking.

This application provides:

* Secure login and registration
* Real-time transaction processing
* Persistent data storage
* User-friendly graphical interface

All financial operations are recorded and stored in a relational database, ensuring **data integrity and auditability**.

---

# 2. OBJECTIVES AND KEY CONCEPTS COVERED

##  Objectives

* Develop a GUI-based banking application using Java Swing
* Implement secure authentication with validation
* Perform core banking operations (Deposit, Withdraw, Transfer)
* Store and manage data using MySQL
* Track transaction and login history
